


--------------------
--  CODING STYLE  --
--------------------

c style:
-> awk

comment:

name functions: (minuscule) for public functions
-> name file + _ + functionnality
ex: log_trace in file log.c

Space:
2 spaces enter between each functions

Separate functions public and private

functions callback: __ at the beginning



----------------
--  LOG INFO  --
----------------

Log type:
-> error
-> debug
-> info

Code color:
-> red: error log
-> green: debug log
-> blue: info log

Format log:
Log type + date + calling function (name file, name functions and line number) + message
ex:
LOG_ERROR [13/10/2014 11:05]: (main.c detect_error l45) PANIC

Log level:
0 -> show no log
1 -> show info log
2 -> show debug log
3 -> show error log
4 -> show error and debug log
5 -> show all log

-----------------------------
--  ARCHITECTURE SOFTWARE  --
-----------------------------

File d'actions:
-> action type
-> action function
-> action priority

